tains a blend of natural oils including Avocado Oil, jojoba oil, Castor Oil and sweet almond oil, enhanced with Vegan Fragrance oils for Scent.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">How often should I use beard oil?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>For best results, apply beard oil daily to soften and moisturize your beard and the skin beneath.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Can I use beard oil on a short beard?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes, our beard oil is suitable for beards of all lengths. It helps to nourish the skin and keep shorter beard hair soft and well-managed.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Is your beard oil suitable for sensitive skin?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes, it's designed to be gentle and is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. However, we recommend patch testing if you're concerned about allergies.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Does your Beard Oil contain nuts?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes as we use Sweet Almond Carrier oil in our Beard Oil.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Is your Beard Oil Vegan and Cruetly Free? <\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes, our 30ml beard oil is both vegan and cruelty-free. We are committed to using only plant-based ingredients and \nSynethetic Fragrance oils, ensuring no animals are harmed or used in the production process. Additionally, our products are not tested on animals at any stage of product development. We are dedicated to providing high-quality, ethical products for our customers<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Scent List Description<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Billion<\/strong> (Inspired by the aftershave ONE Million): Top notes of grapefruit, blood orange, and rose, spiced with cinnamon and mint. Base notes include patchouli, amber, and leather.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Invictors<\/strong> (Aftershave-inspired scent): Primary notes of fresh grapefruit, bay leaf, and Hedione jasmine, with a woody base of patchouli, oak moss, and ambergris.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Kreed<\/strong> (Best seller, inspired by popular aftershave): Primary notes include pineapple, bergamot, oakmoss, vanilla, and musk.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Savage<\/strong> (Inspired by popular aftershave): Primary notes of bergamot, Ambroxan, lavender, vetiver, and patchouli.<\/li>\n<li><strong>The Boss<\/strong> (Woody Spicy fragrance for men): Top notes are Apple, Plum, Bergamot, Lemon, Oakmoss and Geranium; middle notes are Cinnamon, Mahogany and Carnation; base notes are Vanilla, Sandalwood, Cedar, Vetiver and Olive Tree.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Tobacco & Vanilla<\/strong>: A blend of sweet tobacco, warm spices, and a hint of cognac, grounded on a base of smoky wooden oak.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Woodland Elixir<\/strong> (Woody and smooth fragrance for men): Top notes are Cherry, Pear, Ginger; middle notes are Sage and Basil; base notes are Vanilla, Amber and Patchouli.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<script>\nvar acc = document.getElementsByClassName(\"accordion\");\nvar i;\n\nfor (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {\n  acc[i].addEventListener(\"click\", function() {\n    this.classList.toggle(\"active\");\n    var panel = this.nextElementSibling;\n    if (panel.style.maxHeight) {\n      panel.style.maxHeight = null;\n    } else {\n      panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + \"px\";\n    }\n  });\n}\n<\/script>"}},"custom_73yPTR":{"type":"custom","settings":{"code":"<!-- 60ml Beard Oil FAQ -->\n<div class=\"beard-oil-faq-container\">\n    <h2>60ml Beard Oil FAQ<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What is the 2025 nut-free formula for the 60ml Beard Oil?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                Our 2025 60ml Beard Oil features a nut-free formula designed for hydration, nourishment, and styling. It contains:<br>\n                • Jojoba Oil: Hydrates and softens the beard.<br>\n                • Meadowfoam Seed Oil: Locks in moisture for long-lasting softness.<br>\n                • Squalane: Provides lightweight hydration without greasiness.<br>\n                • Coco-Caprylate: Improves hair texture and adds shine.<br>\n                • Sea Buckthorn Oil: Packed with vitamins to promote healthy growth.<br>\n                • Castor Oil: Thickens and strengthens beard hairs.<br>\n                • Buriti Oil: Rich in antioxidants for added protection.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What are the key benefits of the 60ml Beard Oil?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Hydration: Deeply moisturizes your beard, preventing dryness and itchiness.<br>\n                • Nourishment: Promotes healthier and fuller beard growth.<br>\n                • Styling: Adds a polished look and subtle shine.<br>\n                • Sensitivity-Friendly: Nut-free formula suitable for all skin types.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What scents are available in the 60ml Beard Oil?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Billion: Citrus, mint, and leather notes.<br>\n                • Invictors: Fresh grapefruit and jasmine.<br>\n                • Kreed: Pineapple, vanilla, and musk.<br>\n                • Savage: Bergamot and patchouli.<br>\n                • Tobacco & Vanilla: Sweet tobacco and warm vanilla.<br>\n                • Woodland Elixir: Forest-inspired freshness.<br>\n                • The Boss: Woody, spicy with apple, cinnamon, and vanilla.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">How do I use the 60ml Beard Oil?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Wash and towel-dry your beard.<br>\n                • Dispense 3–5 drops into your palm (adjust to beard length).<br>\n                • Rub hands together to warm the oil.<br>\n                • Massage evenly through your beard from roots to tips.<br>\n                • Comb through for a groomed finish.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">How long does a 60ml bottle last?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>Typically 3–4 months with daily use, longer if used sparingly.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What makes the 60ml Beard Oil unique?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Exclusive matte black skull bottle.<br>\n                • Balanced formula providing hydration without greasiness.<br>\n                • Nut-free and vegan-friendly (except certain fragrances).\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">Can the 60ml Beard Oil help with beard growth?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>Ingredients like Castor Oil and Sea Buckthorn Oil promote healthier hair growth over time.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">Is the 60ml Beard Oil recyclable?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>Yes, the glass skull bottle and pipette are recyclable. Separate the pipette components before recycling.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/beardandbones.co.uk\/pages\/faq-2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1E90FF;\">Learn more<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.beard-oil-faq-container {\n    bac